<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='885540' id='t-885540'>Chris Anderson: Thank you. Just a quick question.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='889508' id='t-889508'>The latest numbers on the die-off of bees,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='892664' id='t-892664'>is there any sign of things bottoming out?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='894892' id='t-894892'>What's your hope/depression level on this?</span>
