<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='898285' id='t-898285'>At least in the United States,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='900238' id='t-900238'>an average of 30 percent of all bee hives</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='902590' id='t-902590'>are lost every winter.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='904717' id='t-904717'>About 20 years ago,</span>
